##working with maps
install.packages("maps")
install.packages("mapdata")
library(maps)
library(mapdata)
map('world')
map('lakes', add=TRUE, fill=TRUE, col='white', boundary='black')

Ref:  http://www.molecularecologist.com/2012/09/making-maps-with-r/

##working with google map
For google map do the followings

install.packages("RgoogleMaps")
install.packages("grid")
install.packages("ggmap")
install.packages("ggplot2")
install.packages("RgoogleMaps")

then as per the followings site.

http://yarkerconsulting.com/index.php/blog/15-google-maps-and-r
